d:
This is a collection of images, some that made it into the comic and some that didn’t. Here you can see the transformation path of the main character’s body from one of my comics.

As a note, considering the general opinion here, I don’t see myself as an artist, nor do I consider these images to be “art.” My drawing skills aren’t strong enough to bring my ideas to life in a way I wouldn’t be embarrassed to show, but AI can do that. I’m glad I can use it to assemble these images into a story.
I might expand the gallery in the future, but not all images are suitable for publication and need to be sorted through.

Comic https://e-hentai.org/g/3607393/6c1e68d61c/

You can use my site if you need a comfortable place to read comics. https://sirnrei.com/
There's a little more on my patreon, but usually comics become free in the future. https://www.patreon.com/SirNrei
